{"tid":1413460,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術][抛磚]如何斷狗官米路","createTime":"2019-08-05T09:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T11:50:35.000Z","uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a50cd26dec53033767c755722daf3e563c1aa1c","tid":1413460,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"P牌第一次開po ,麻煩屌細力啲<br />\n夢遊左咁耐,三罷都迫唔到班狗官出聲,我地有无可能另開新夢境？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[抛磚]眾所鳩知,狗官同地產商有勾結,大眾未知會發展的地方,地產商都未卜先知,10幾年前買定響手屯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">而且辣招永遠无撚用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原因如何,相信夢遊者好清楚<br />\n如果地產商有咩事,班高官就斷左財路,同時班鄉紳都會中招,所以我求大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>搞地產商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">麻煩巴絲屌細力啲</span>"},{"pid":"444dbe6a2b43c295bf5a09cebcb091be3919abb3","tid":1413460,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:00:01.000Z","msg":"自頂"},{"pid":"7ada137d85e19a36364642411f213083f536b3a3","tid":1413460,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:00:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9c66477c7b2399cec75e2562f735cc5a72f7f3a1","tid":1413460,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:00:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"852e50055bd04268c412ce34514d9d887eb0ae8f","tid":1413460,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"3a12164c17e398ef29ae6b7bb3458b07a471af3f","tid":1413460,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0